=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex64 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark pure_tone sound, with fm_or_inharmonic oscillator character around 996 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 996.3597
  harmonic_decay_rate: -6.3736
  harmonic_regularity: 0.5700
  pitch_clarity: 96.0996
  inharmonicity: 0.2392
  type: fm_or_inharmonic
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -6.6151
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
